---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import { SITE_NAME, PHONE_NUMBER } from '../../utils/constants';
import { generateServiceSchema } from '../../utils/schema';

const schema = generateServiceSchema({
  name: 'Professional Tree Trimming & Pruning',
  description: 'Expert tree trimming and pruning to enhance tree health and appearance in Birmingham, AL',
  provider: SITE_NAME
});

const pageTitle = 'Professional Tree Trimming & Pruning in Birmingham, AL | Expert Arborists';
const pageDescription = 'Professional tree trimming and pruning services. Enhance tree health, improve appearance, and ensure safety. Licensed arborists serving Birmingham.';
---

<Base title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)} />

  <!-- Hero Image -->
  <section class="bg-white py-0">
    <img src="/images/services/tree-trimming-hero.png" alt="Professional arborist pruning large tree on upscale residential estate" class="w-full h-96 object-cover object-center" />
  </section>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-700 to-green-900 text-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Professional Tree Trimming & Pruning</h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-green-100 mb-8">
            Expert trimming and pruning to enhance tree health, improve appearance, and ensure safety. Our certified arborists use proven techniques for optimal results.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a
              href={`tel:${PHONE_NUMBER}`}
              class="bg-white text-green-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-gray-100 transition text-center"
            >
              Call Now for Free Quote
            </a>
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-white hover:text-green-700 transition text-center"
            >
              Request Online
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-green-600 rounded-lg p-8">
          <p class="text-green-100 text-lg leading-relaxed">Professional trimming extends tree lifespan by 10-15 years and improves structural integrity while enhancing curb appeal.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Benefits Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Benefits of Professional Tree Trimming</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">✓ Enhanced Tree Health</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Strategic removal of dead, diseased, and crossing branches improves air circulation throughout the canopy and stimulates vigorous new growth. Healthier trees are more resilient to pests and disease. Professional trimming identifies and removes problem branches before they compromise the entire tree.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">🌳 Improved Safety</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Eliminates hazardous branches that could fail during storms and damage your home, vehicles, or property. Our arborists identify weak branch angles, internal decay, and structural defects that threaten safety. Regular trimming reduces liability and prevents accidents before they happen.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">📈 Structural Strength</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Proper pruning techniques create stronger branch structures with superior angles that resist splitting and storm damage. By removing heavy branches competing for resources, we redirect growth into stronger limbs that support tree longevity and stability.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">🏡 Increased Curb Appeal</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Well-trimmed trees dramatically enhance your home's appearance and landscape aesthetics. Studies show quality landscaping, including well-maintained trees, can increase property value by 5-10%. A professionally trimmed tree becomes a focal point that elevates the entire property.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">☀️ More Sunlight</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Crown thinning opens the canopy to allow more sunlight to reach your lawn, gardens, and landscaping below. This increases grass health, allows flowering plants to thrive, and improves the overall outdoor environment of your property.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">⚡ Prevents Overgrowth</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Regular trimming prevents branches from growing into power lines, roofing, gutters, and siding—avoiding expensive damage and potential safety hazards. Proactive maintenance is far less costly than emergency repairs caused by overgrown trees.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Trimming Types -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Types of Tree Trimming Services</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Crown Thinning</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Selective removal of branches throughout the crown to reduce density while maintaining the tree's natural shape. This technique improves light penetration, enhances air circulation, and promotes healthier growth. Crown thinning is ideal for dense trees that need more sunlight for lawns below or when structural improvement is needed without dramatically changing the tree's appearance.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Crown Raising</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Removes lower branches to increase clearance above ground, sidewalks, driveways, roofs, and building structures. This service is essential when trees interfere with traffic sightlines, building access, or utility lines. Crown raising maintains tree health while creating functional space underneath the canopy.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Crown Shaping</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Expert sculpting that enhances a tree's natural form while improving overall aesthetics and promoting healthy growth patterns. Crown shaping develops stronger branch structure, improves tree appearance, and can redirect growth away from nearby structures. This technique combines art and science to create beautiful, healthy trees.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Deadwood Removal</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Strategic removal of dead, diseased, and damaged branches that compromise tree appearance and health. Deadwood attracts pests and disease organisms. Removing it immediately improves overall tree health, prevents pest spread to healthy portions, and eliminates potential safety hazards from brittle branches that could fall.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Our Professional Trimming Process</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-green-600 text-white font-bold">1</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Consultation & Assessment</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">We conduct a thorough evaluation of tree health, species characteristics, growth patterns, your property goals, and any specific concerns. This assessment informs our customized trimming strategy. We discuss your vision and develop a plan that achieves your objectives while prioritizing tree health.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-green-600 text-white font-bold">2</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Expert Pruning</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Our certified arborists use proven cutting techniques to remove selected branches while preserving the tree's natural shape and structural integrity. We make precise cuts at branch collars, remove branches in optimal sequences, and maintain proper branch angles. Every cut is strategic and promotes tree health.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-green-600 text-white font-bold">3</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Clean-Up & Debris Removal</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">All branches, twigs, and debris are cleaned up and removed from your property. We leave your yard pristine and ready to enjoy. Wood chips can be left for mulch or removed entirely—your preference.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="bg-green-900 text-white py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Schedule Your Tree Trimming Today</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-green-100 mb-8">
        Our certified arborists will assess your trees and provide expert recommendations for optimal health and appearance.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href={`tel:${PHONE_NUMBER}`}
          class="bg-white text-green-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-gray-100 transition text-lg"
        >
          Call {PHONE_NUMBER}
        </a>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-white hover:text-green-900 transition text-lg"
        >
          Request Free Quote
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
